N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 42.3 - Board of managers

State Regulations

All laboratories shall be under the supervision, direction and control of either a board of managers or the board of health appointed in accordance with section
523
of the Public Health Law. Notes
